issue.body:
Hi,

Is there a way to suppress the validation when the input field is disabled?

```
<input
    className="form-control"
    type="text"
    name={`action${j}`}
    id={param.name}
    onChange={e => setValue(e.target.name, e.target.value, true)}
    disabled={name !== selectedAction}
    ref={register({
         required: "This field is required",
         pattern: {
              value: new RegExp(param.regex),
              message: `${param.errorMessage}`
       })}
/>
```
Thank you.
